snippet.title: Joe Danger!
snippet.description:
Trailer for Joe Danger! A new download title coming in Spring 2010.
Wear the cape of the World's Most Determined Stuntman. Race against your Rivals, out-thrill your friends and defy death to defeat the dastardly Team Nasty.
Joe Danger is being made by four friends who together are Hello Games. Check out them out at http://www.hellogames.org or follow them at http://twitter.com/hellogames.
